-bloodfinale/27176|title=True Blood finale audience doubles last season's ender|publisher=TVbytheNumbers|date=September 15, 2009 |accessdate=September 14, 2010}}</ref>\n! style=\"font-size:smaller\"| 2009\n! style=\"background:#fc9;\"|4.28\n|-\n! '''[[True Blood (season 3)|Season 3]]'''\n! 12\n| style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:110%\"|<center>June 13, 2010</center>\n! 5.10<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.com/2010/06/15/hbos-true-blood-premiere-ratings-up-38/54173 |title=HBO's 'True Blood' Premiere Ratings Up 38% \u2013 TV Ratings, Nielsen Ratings, Television Show Ratings |publisher=TVbytheNumbers.com |date=June 15, 2010 |accessdate=June 29, 2010}}</ref>\n| style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:110%\"|<center>September 12, 2010</center>\n! 5.38<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/|title=TV By The Numbers by zap2it.com|publisher=|accessdate=March 15, 2017}}</ref>\n! style=\"font-size:smaller\"| 2010\n! style=\"background:#fc9;\"|4.97\n|-\n! '''[[True Blood (season 4)|Season 4]]'''\n! 12\n| style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:110%\"|<center>June 26, 2011</center>\n! 5.42\n| style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:110%\"|<center>September 11, 2011</center>\n! 5.05\n! style=\"font-size:smaller\"| 2011\n! style=\"background:#fc9;\"|4.97\n|-\n! '''[[True Blood (season 5)|Season 5]]'''\n! 12\n| style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:110%\"|<center>June 10, 2012</center>\n! 5.20<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/06/12/sunday-cable-ratings-true-blood-wins-night-mad-men-longmire-the-client-list-the-glades-drop-dead-diva-more/137638/|title=Sunday Cable Ratings: 'True Blood' Wins Night, 'Mad Men', 'Longmire', 'The Client List', 'The Glades', 'Drop Dead Diva' & More|work=TV by the Numbers|last=Bibel|first=Sara|date=June 12, 2012|accessdate=June 12, 2012}}</ref>\n| style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:110%\"|<center>August 26, 2012</center>\n! 5.05\n! style=\"font-size:smaller\"| 2012\n! style=\"background:#fc9;\"|4.67\n|-\n! '''[[True Blood (sea