 don't list this--->\n<!---* Gag reel. The sources don't list this--->\n* A Conversation with Andrew Kreisberg and Kevin Smith\n* Supergirl Lives Audio Commentary featuring Andrew Kreisberg and Kevin Smith\n* Did You Know facts for fans\n* Featurettes\n** ''Supergirl: Alien Fight Night''\n** ''Aliens Among Us''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | 3\n| September 18, 2018<ref name=\"HomeMedia-SupergirlS3\">{{cite web |title=Supergirl: The Complete Third Season |url=https://www.amazon.com/Supergirl-Complete-Third-Season-Blu-ray/dp/B077697MTC/ |website=Amazon |access-date=September 12, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181126180932/https://www.amazon.com/Supergirl-Complete-Third-Season-Blu-ray/dp/B077697MTC |archive-date=November 26, 2018 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n| September 17, 2018<ref name=\"R2S3Release\">{{cite web |url=https://www.amazon.co.uk/Supergirl-Season-DVD-Jesse-Warn/dp/B07DQ2PWT3/ |title=Supergirl \u2013 Season 3 [DVD] [2018] |work=Amazon |accessdate=September 12, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190323012115/https://www.amazon.co.uk/Supergirl-Season-DVD-Jesse-Warn/dp/B07DQ2PWT3 |archive-date=March 23, 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n| September 19, 2018<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.jbhifi.com.au/movies-tv-shows/movies-tv-shows-on-sale/tv-drama/supergirl-season-3/322081/ |title=Supergirl \u2013 Season 3 |work=JBHiFi |accessdate=September 12, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180912092026/https://www.jbhifi.com.au/movies-tv-shows/movies-tv-shows-on-sale/tv-drama/supergirl-season-3/322081/ |archive-date=September 12, 2018 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n| September 18, 2018<ref name=\"HomeMedia-SupergirlS3\" />\n| September 17, 2018<ref name=\"R2S3Release\" />\n| style=\"text-align:left\" | \n* All four episodes of the [[Crisis on Earth-X]] crossover\n* 2017 Comic-Con panel<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/tv/news/948749-supergirl-season-3-blu-ray-and-dvd-details-announced |title=Supergirl Season 3 Blu-ray and DVD Details Announced! |last=Hemmert |first=Kylie |date=May 29, 2018 |work=[[comingsoon.net]] |accessdate=September 13, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180913223300/http://www.comingsoon.net/tv/news/948749-supergirl-season-3-blu-ray-and-dvd-details-announced |archive-date=September 13, 2018 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n* Deleted scenes\n* Gag reel\n* Inside the Crossover: Crisis on Earth-X\n* Featurettes\n** ''She Will Reign!''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | 4\n| September 17, 2019<ref>{{cite web |title=Supergirl: The Complete Fourth Season |url=https://www.amazon.com/Supergirl-Complete-Fourth-Season-DVD/dp/B07Q8Q7BDK/ref=mp_s_a_1_7?keywords=Supergirl+season+4&qid=1569164808&sr=8-7|website=Amazon}}</ref>\n|\n|\n| September 23, 2019<ref>{{cite web |title=Supergirl: The Complete Fourth Season |url=https://www.amazon.com/Supergirl-Season-4-Blu-ray/dp/B07TLMV635/ref=mp_s_a_1_9?keywords=Supergirl+season+4&qid=1569165041&sr=8-9|website=Amazon}}</ref>\n| \n| style=\"text-align:left\" | \n* All three episodes of the [[Elseworlds]] crossover (Blu-ray)\n* The Best of DC TV's Comic-Con Panel San Diego 2018\n* Inside the Crossover: Elseworlds\n* Gag reel\n* Deleted scenes\n* Featurettes\n** ''Villains: Modes of Persuasion''\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n<!-- Please do not delete the following reference. When it is not being used, comment it out to avoid the need to recreate it.\n<ref name=tfc>{{cite web |url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/showatch/supergirl/ |title=Shows A-Z \u2013 Supergirl |work=[[The Futon Critic]] |publisher=Futon Media |accessdate=December 4, 2015}}</ref> -->\n{{Refbegin}}\n;General references <!-- These references will apply to most, if not all, episodes -->\n* {{cite web |url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/showatch/supergirl/ |title=Shows A-Z \u2013 Supergirl |work=[[The Futon Critic]] |publisher=Futon Media |accessdate=December 4, 2015}}\n{{Refend}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Wikiquote}}\n* {{Official website}} (only available in the United States)\n